OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fairly bright day with some
OL,6,Fsunny intervals. A few showers,
OL,7,Fespecially near the east coast later
OL,8,Fin the day. Winds will be mostly light.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FStill the odd shower this
OL,11,Fevening then becoming dry with some
OL,12,Fgood clear spells developing tonight.
OL,13,FQuite cold with perhaps a touch of
OL,14,Ffrost in sheltered spots.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FA mainly dry day with some
OL,17,Fbright or sunny intervals the best of
OL,18,Fthese around the coasts. One or two
OL,19,Fscattered showers are possible. A
OL,20,Fcolder day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
