OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells much of Sunday then
OL,7,Flight rain spreading from northwest.
OL,8,FMonday dry and bright then some patchy
OL,9,Fevening rain. Sunny spells and a few
OL,10,Fshowers on Tuesday.
